aystationlifestyle.net/2014/02/10/playstation-vita-to-get-over-100-games-in-2014/|title=PlayStation Vita to Get "Over 100 Games" in 2014: The Wolf Among Us, Invizimals, and More Highlighted|last=Dunning|first=Jason|work=playstationlifestyle.net|date=2014-02-10|accessdate=2014-04-05|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307204141/https://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2014/02/10/playstation-vita-to-get-over-100-games-in-2014/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]、[[PlayStation_Vita|PlayStation Vita]]、[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]主机平台零售版于2014年11月发布。
